{"lemma":"مَصَحُّ","slug":"مَصَحُّ","root":"ص.ح.ح","root_slug":"ص-ح-ح","root_link":"/words/roots/ص-ح-ح","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":false},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n23770","n23847","n38637"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D9%85%D9%8E%D8%B5%D9%8E%D8%AD%D9%8F%D9%91"}},"translations":null,"definition":null,"etymology":null,"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n23770","headword_ar":"مُصِحٌّ","root":"SH","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"A man"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"having his family and his cattle in a healthy,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"sound, state;"},{"kind":"text","text":"whether he himself be in health or sick: (L:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"having his cattle in a healthy,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"sound, state, after their having been affected by a plague,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"murrain,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"distemper:"},{"kind":"text","text":"pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"muSiH~uwna","text_ar":"مُصِحُّونَ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (S, L.) It is said in a trad.,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"laA","text_ar":"لَا"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yuwridan~a *uw EaAhapK EalaY muSiH~K","text_ar":"يُورِدَنَّ ذُو عَاهَةٍ عَلَى مُصِحٍّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, L) i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"One whose camels are affected by a murrain,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"distemper, shall by no means bring them to water immediately after one whose camels are in a healthy,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"sound, state,"},{"kind":"text","text":"so as to water the former beasts with the latter: a prohibition apparently given for fear that the latter beasts should become diseased like the former, and it should be supposed that the disease had passed by contagion, which ought not to be imagined. (L. [See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mumoriDN","text_ar":"مُمْرِضٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":".])"}],"source_refs":["L","S"]},{"entry_id":"n23847","headword_ar":"مُصْحٍ","root":"SHw","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"; and its fem."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"muSoHiyapN","text_ar":"مُصْحِيَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SaHowN","text_ar":"صَحْوٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n38637","headword_ar":"مَصَحَ","root":"mSH","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"muSuwHN","text_ar":"مُصُوحٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maSoHN","text_ar":"مَصْحٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", TA),"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(a thing, S,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"went away; passed away; departed."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K.) ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"It finished; came to an end; ceased."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K.) ―         -b3-"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"It"},{"kind":"text","text":"(a garment)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became old and worn-out."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K.) ―         -b4-"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"It"},{"kind":"text","text":"(a plant)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became faded in its blossoms."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K.) ―         -b5-  Also, inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"muSuwHN","text_ar":"مُصُوحٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"It"},{"kind":"text","text":"(a blossom)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"faded;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"lost its colour."},{"kind":"text","text":"(AHn.) ―         -b6-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maSaHa","text_ar":"مَصَحَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"muSuwHN","text_ar":"مُصُوحٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"It"},{"kind":"text","text":"(the shade)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became short."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K.) ―         -b7-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maSaHa","text_ar":"مَصَحَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"muSuwHN","text_ar":"مُصُوحٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"It"},{"kind":"text","text":"(an udder)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"ceased to have milk."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ―         -b8-"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"It"},{"kind":"text","text":"(the milk of a camel)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"ceased; passed away."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K.) ―         -b9-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maSiHa","text_ar":"مَصِحَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"It"},{"kind":"text","text":"(shade)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became deficient and thin."},{"kind":"text","text":"So accord. to the K; but in other lexicons, the verb, with reference to shade, is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maSaHa","text_ar":"مَصَحَ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.) ―         -b10-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maSaHa","text_ar":"مَصَحَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"muSuwHN","text_ar":"مُصُوحٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"It"},{"kind":"text","text":"(a writing)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became obliterated,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"nearly so."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ―         -b11-"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"It"},{"kind":"text","text":"(a dwelling)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became obliterated;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"its vestiges became effaced."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ―         -b12-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maSaHa bihi","text_ar":"مَصَحَ بِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, K,) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^amoSaHahu","text_ar":"اَمْصَحَهُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (IB,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He took away, carried off,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"went away with, it;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"caused it to go, go away,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"pass away."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, IB, K.) ―         -b13-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maSaHa fiY AlA^aroDi","text_ar":"مَصَحَ فِى الاَرْضِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maSoHN","text_ar":"مَصْحٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He set forth journeying through the land,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"earth:"},{"kind":"text","text":"as also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"masaHa","text_ar":"مَسَحَ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (ISd.)"}],"source_refs":["S","K","IB"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}